 Objective function 2000x + 800y  minimize
 c) Conditions 8x + 10y ≤ 60, 6x + 3y ≤ 40, x ≥ 0, y ≥ 0
 Objective function 2000x + 800y  minimize
 d) Conditions 8x + 10y ≥ 60, 6x + 3y ≤ 40, x ≥ 0, y ≥ 0
 Objective function 2000x + 800y  minimize

